more healthily again.

02:33.320 --> 02:35.360
Oh, not beetroot brownies again.

02:35.360 --> 02:37.160
What's wrong with my beetroot
brownies?

02:37.160 --> 02:40.320
Brownies are supposed to be brownie,
not purply.

02:40.320 --> 02:43.680
It's not the only thing that was
supposed to be brownie that
went purply.

02:43.680 --> 02:48.400
We're going to the health
store in the morning,
after we've done the school run.

02:48.400 --> 02:49.880
"We"♪ Yes, "we".

02:49.880 --> 02:54.000
If you think it's so easy to talk
to the Lollipop Man, you can do it.

02:54.000 --> 02:56.440
OK, I will. Good.

02:56.440 --> 02:58.920
I don't think you realise how
difficult it is to say no to

02:58.920 --> 03:01.320
a sweet old man who's just
trying to be friendly.

03:01.320 --> 03:03.640
