with the search.

03:50.000 --> 03:53.360
Ha! I bet the kids love having
a fun dad like you.

03:53.360 --> 03:56.000
Yeah, it's a
laugh a minute in our house,

03:56.000 --> 03:58.520
followed by 59 seconds of arguing.

03:58.520 --> 04:00.200
Look, there's something
I wanted to say.

04:00.200 --> 04:03.400
You know the lollies...
There is no need for thank-yous.

04:03.400 --> 04:07.280
To be honest, I think
I get more out of it.

04:07.280 --> 04:10.800
The kiddies'
sunny smiles make my day.

04:10.800 --> 04:14.440
And what's a lollipop man
without lollipops, eh?

04:16.200 --> 04:19.720
Actually, there's, um,
something I wanted to ask you.

04:19.720 --> 04:21.160
Yes, son?

04:21.160 --> 04:23.720
Will you adopt me♪ Ha.

04:23.720 --> 04:24.960
No, that's not it.

04:26.000 --> 04:29.960
The kids love the lollies, it's very
generous of you, thank you.

04:29.960 --> 04:32.600
It's a lovely thing you're doing.
Well, thank you.

04:32.600 --> 04:35.680
And don't worry,
I know what you want to say.

04:35.680 --> 04:40.360
I mean, parents come up to me
all the time, it's not a problem.

04:40.360 --> 04:43.960
Really?
Of course you can have a lollipop.

04:46.480 --> 04:48.920
The thing is... Yes?

04:48.920 --> 04:51.680
It's just that some parents,

04:51.680 --> 04:55.400
they might think it's inappropriate,

04:55.400 --> 04:56.880
you know, receiving sweets...

04:59.160 --> 05:01.000
..from strangers.

05:01.000 --> 05:03.080
Oh, dear.

05:03.080 --> 05:05.960
I never really
thought of it like that.

05:05.960 --> 05:10.040
Since my hip operation, I've not
been as active as I used to be,

05:10.040 --> 05:14.200
and giving the little ones a lolly
and seeing their faces light up

05:14.200 --> 05:19.320
is one of the few pleasures that
I have left in life.

05:20.640 --> 05:21.840
I'm so very sorry.

05:23.440 --> 05:24.600
I feel awful.

05:25.520 --> 05:28.920
Well, hang on, let me finish
what I was saying.

05:28.920 --> 05:32.560
Some parents might think that,
but they are idiots,

05:32.560 --> 05:34.800
because we think it's great.

05:34.800 --> 05:36.760
All the parents round here do.

05:36.760 --> 05:40.280
You are the best lollipop man
in the world.

05:40.280 --> 05:41.600
Really♪ Yes.

05:42.720 --> 05:44.880
You've made my day.

05:44.880 --> 05:47.120
You really have.

05:47.120 --> 05:48.640
In fact, as a treat,

05:48.640 --> 05:51.840
your kids are going to get double
helpings from now on.

05:53.080 --> 05:57.120
Oh, good. I'll tell my wife,
she'll be absolutely delighted.

05:57.120 --> 06:01.320
And don't forget to clean
your teeth afterwards.

06:01.320 --> 06:03.400
We don't want them falling out.

06:03.400 --> 06:05.840
Don't worry, my wife will be
knocking them out anyway!

06:05.840 --> 06:08.200
HE LAUGHS
You're a funny man!

06:08.200 --> 06:10.400
Ah, thanks. I hate him.

06:18.680 --> 06:22.520
Fancy some butternut squash cake,
Anna♪ It's gluten-free.

06:22.520 --> 06:26.200
