from our house to the school gates

07:26.000 --> 07:29.600
strapped into a top-of-the-range,
hypo-allergenic booster seat,

07:29.600 --> 07:32.840
in the back of a BMW designed
to withstand a land mine blast.

07:34.040 --> 07:37.120
I suppose we just
love our child more.

07:38.720 --> 07:41.000
