it's too harsh.

09:36.760 --> 09:37.960
I was going to put,

09:37.960 --> 09:40.720
"We are curious as to whether
our lovely lollipop man is

09:40.720 --> 09:44.160
"breaking any rules by generously
giving out lollipops to the kids."

09:44.160 --> 09:47.480
Do you want him
to stop or get an OBE?

09:47.480 --> 09:50.200
