'completely fine about it'."

10:15.920 --> 10:19.000
Do you know what,
why don't you write it?

10:19.000 --> 10:20.400
All right, I will.

10:20.400 --> 10:22.440
"Dear Sir..." Slash Madam. I know!

10:28.480 --> 10:31.840
Mum♪ Why doesn't this cereal
